{{define "content"}}
<div class="bg-white px-6 py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600">
            Legal
        </p>

        <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            Privacy Policy
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8">
            This website is a non-commercial hobby project based in the USA.
            Access to this website is restricted to TribeNet players only.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
                Personal Data
            </h2>

            <p class="mt-6">
                This website does not collect any personal data.
            </p>

            <br>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
                Game Data
            </h2>

            <p class="mt-6">
                Your game data is stored on the server and is not shared with any third parties.
                Every player's data is stored in separate folders.
                Access is password protected and restricted to the server owner and the players themselves.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-6">
                You can remove all non-movement data from your reports before uploading them.
                The parser ignores that data, so it never impacts map generation.
            </p>

            <br>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
                What do we collect?
            </h2>

            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                         aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M10 18a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 0 0-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.137-.089l4-5.5Z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>
                            <strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Cookies</strong>
                            <br>
                            We use cookies to store your session data.
                            This is necessary to control access to data on the site.
                            If you disable cookies, you will not be able to access most of the site.
                        </span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                         aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M10 18a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 0 0-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.137-.089l4-5.5Z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>
                            <strong class="font-semibold text-gray-900">IP addresses</strong>
                            <br>
                            The server uses Nginx to serve the site.
                            Nginx logs IP addresses for security and abuse detection.
                            The logs are deleted after 30 days.
                        </span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{{end}}
